2803Naārammaṇapaccayā…  naadhipatipaccayā (sahajātasadisaṃ)…  naanantarapaccayā…  nasamanantarapaccayā…  naaññamaññapaccayā…  naupanissayapaccayā…  napurejātapaccayā (paṭiccavārasadisaṃ)…  napacchājātapaccayā…  naāsevanapaccayā…  nakammapaccayā…pe…  navippayuttapaccayā (paṭiccavārapaccanīye vippayuttasadisaṃ)…  nonatthipaccayā…  novigatapaccayā… .
